"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1927851-Andy-Murray-Olympics-2024-tennis-withdrawal\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Andy Murray'swithdrawal from the2024 Olympicsmen's singles tennis tournament in Paris has caused chaos at Roland Garros as the Briton prepares to call time on his professional career.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7380960627906397e-59, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 82, \"end\": 87, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 8.004210936060817e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray was included in Team GB's squad for the tournament, which begins on August 2 with the men's doubles.\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 187, \"end\": 193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9959682053793505e-39, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 210, \"end\": 217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999929186597618, \"rank\": 5.501253637322566e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But despite entering into the singles' draw, the 37-year-olddropped out to concentrateon participating in the doubles' alongside his partner, Dan Evans.\", \"from\": 296, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 438, \"end\": 447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999579126491286, \"rank\": 4.208912019158757e-05, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 552, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  His decision to pull out caused a delay for Olympic Games organisers, who were due to host the draw from 10am (BST) in France but were 20 minutes late in kicking things off.\", \"from\": 584, \"to\": 781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 719, \"end\": 722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.141865531864262e-15, \"text\": \"BST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\"}, {\"begin\": 727, \"end\": 733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.5730048928401366, \"rank\": 0.6220535599884194, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the draw concluded, an empty slot showed up on the screen titled 'Alternate AAA', which is likely to have been caused by Murray's removal from the singles' reckoning.\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 907, \"end\": 913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9959682053793505e-39, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In this case, the 'alternate' player was drawn to face Sebastian Ofner of Germany.\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1008, \"end\": 1023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Ofner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sebastian Ofner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Ofner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Ofner\"}, {\"begin\": 1027, \"end\": 1034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9428985522094934, \"rank\": 0.04601136125319993, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the proceedings may have been delayed, it was worth the wait as far as tennis fans were concerned after being handed a potential treat in the second round of the draw.\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1256, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1321, \"end\": 1326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 8.004210936060817e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1402, \"end\": 1414, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9997316928263976, \"rank\": 0.0002683790459750396, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Novak Djokovic and Rafael Nadal will meet in round two at Roland Garros if they emerge unscathed from their first round matches.\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1489, \"end\": 1503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 1508, \"end\": 1520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 14-time French Open winner Nadal takes on Hungarian player Marton Fucsovics, while Djokovic faces Matthew Ebden in round one.\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1748, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1650, \"end\": 1655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999054126, \"rank\": 9.442326330477997e-11, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 1665, \"end\": 1674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungarian_language\", \"score\": 0.7395553671975492, \"rank\": 0.3507722086045008, \"text\": \"Hungarian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungarian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungarian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1682, \"end\": 1698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rton_Fucsovics\", \"score\": 0.9999999956035026, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marton Fucsovics\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rton_Fucsovics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M\\u00e1rton_Fucsovics\"}, {\"begin\": 1706, \"end\": 1714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.1322763554369087e-12, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 1721, \"end\": 1734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Ebden\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matthew Ebden\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Ebden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Ebden\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That may have left the three-time Grand Slam winner to consider what might have been in his final tennis tournament, especially with a winnable tie against Ofner.\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But in explaining his decision to remove himself from the singles' draw, Murray admitted that he is unable to cope with so many matches in such a short space of time.\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 2080, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1987, \"end\": 1993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9959682053793505e-39, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously me and Dan have made the commitment to each other that [doubles) was what we were going to prioritise,\\\" Murray said.\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2211, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2199, \"end\": 2205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9959682053793505e-39, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That gives the team and us the best opportunity to get a medal, realistically.\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2292, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My back is still not perfect and the potential of playing two matches in a day is maybe not the best.\\\"\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2395, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2506, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2616, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  In the doubles' draw, Murray and Evans will be pitted up against the Japanese pairing of Kei Nishikori and Taro Daniel.\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2663, \"end\": 2669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9959682053793505e-39, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://